  <text>
    <body>
      <pb n="1" />
        <opener>
          <dateline>
            <date when="1873-06-09">June 9th 3</date>
          </dateline>
          <salute>Dear <persName ref="#stillca">Katie</persName></salute>
        </opener>
        <p>
          Your letter of the 6th<lb/> inst. reached me on the 7th, and <unclear reason="faded" resp="#jd"/><lb/> have been duly noted.
        </p>
        <p>
	        It is very gratifying to know that<lb/> you were <unclear resp="#fg">treated on even hand</unclear> <unclear reason="faded" resp="#jd"/><lb/> the U.G.R.R. with marked <unclear reason="faded" resp="#jd"/><lb/> so you “feel like trying some<lb/> other place”. I know of <add place="above" rend="carrot">no</add> <del rend="strikethrough"><unclear reason="faded" resp="#jd"/></del> place<lb/> where I think you could do better than<lb/> in <placeName>Syracuse</placeName>. Of course you would<lb/> be some distance from your mother<lb/> yet rail roads bring  <unclear reason="faded" resp="#jd">a place to appear</unclear><lb/> <unclear reason="faded" resp="#jd"/> a good way off only <unclear reason="faded" resp="#jd"/> days <unclear reason="faded" resp="#jd"/><lb/> from home after all. Of course there<lb/> are plenty of places much <unclear reason="faded" resp="#jd">nearer</unclear><lb/> where you could operate.
        </p>
        <p> I have sent your order of books<lb/> by today's express.<lb/></p>
      <table rows="5" cols="2">
        <row role="data"><cell role="data">5 U.G.R.R. paneled @$5.</cell><cell role="data">$25.00</cell></row>
        <row role="data"><cell role="data">4 <unclear>Do</unclear> Eng. Clo. @4.50</cell><cell role="data"><hi rend="underline">18.00</hi></cell></row>
        <row role="data"><cell role="data"></cell><cell role="data">$43.00</cell></row>
        <row role="data"><cell role="data">1/2 off</cell><cell role="data"><hi rend="underline">21.50</hi></cell></row>
        <row role="data"><cell role="data"></cell><cell role="data">21.50</cell></row>
      </table>
          <p>You are doing very <unclear reason="faded" resp="#jd">nicely</unclear> this season<lb/>
          Love to your mother &amp; <persName ref="#stillpe">Peter</persName>
        </p>
        <closer>
          <salute>Yours affect.</salute>
         <signed><persName ref="#stillwi"><choice><abbr>W</abbr><expan>William </expan></choice> Still</persName></signed>
        </closer>
